Module scenebuilder.jobs
Package com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.job.editor

Class JobUtils

java.lang.Object
com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.job.editor.JobUtils
public class JobUtils
extends Object
This class defines getter and setter on FXOM objects without using the modify job. Theses methods are used by jobs that creates new FXOM objects and sets some of their properties. No need to use a job in this case as the undo action will remove the new added FXOM object.
